The Daily Economy article
The usual Christmas basket of the Daily increased by an average of 16 percent in the Buda<0xC3><0xB6>rs trade triangle this year again, but in all hypermarkets the increase in value was well over a thousand forints.
As last December, prices in grocery stores were already “slowing down”, so compared to the previous high base, there was no drastic increase in price.
